4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge who want to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks and includes three live online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 16 students. Participants will gain skills in Windows, Linux, and network administration, as well as cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The curriculum also emphasizes risk management and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an official certification recognized by multiple institutions. More information can be found at [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop